  "dct_description_sm": [
    "South Africa HYPS Inland Water Bodies, 2014 is a polygon theme representing inland water bodies in South Africa. Atrributes include the water body type (dam, dry pan, fish farm, lake, large reservoir, marsh vlei, mud flats, non-perennial pan, perennial pan, pool, purification plant, school area, sewerage works, swamp, water tank). The source material is a 1:50,000 topographical map series. The original shapefile was originally created in tiles and were merged together by Columbia Libraries, the original map sheet for each feature is included in the attribute table."
